  "time_ut": 1660616388,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0daf\u0da9\u0dd4\u0dbd\u0dda\u0db1\u0dcf \u0da2\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dd2\u0d9a \u0dc3\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dba\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d89\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dda \u0dba\u0ddd\u0da2\u0db1\u0dcf\u0dc0 \u0d89\u0dc0\u0dad\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The proposal to remove the Dadulena from the national animal list is rejected",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Minister of Agriculture, Mahinda Amaraweera, has decided not to continue the discussions regarding the removal of Dadulena as the national animal.",
        "It is in consideration of the protest raised in the society regarding the removal of the animal from being named as the national animal.",
        "Due to the fact that Dadulena is an animal that damages crops, there was a discussion recently in the Ministry of Agriculture regarding the removal of that animal from being named as the national animal."
      ],
      "title_ents": [],
      "body_line_ents_list": [
        [
          {
            "text": "Mahinda Amaraweera",
